➜编程之禅：Zen Coding
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=17641	41280
如果你是靠写HTML谋生的，现在还不知道<a href="http://code.google.com/p/zen-coding/">Zen Coding</a>的话，绝对是一大损失，白白浪费了很多敲代码的时间。<i> <a href="http://developers.slashdot.org/story/10/05/02/2116230/Zen-Coding">Zen Coding</a>是一个加速HTML、XML、XSL以及其它结构化代码格式编程的编辑器插件，语法类似CSS。目前支持的代码编辑环境包括：Aptana/Eclipse、TextMate、Notepad++等。Zen Coding的核心是一个强大的缩写引擎，可以很容易将缩写扩展成完整的HTML代码表达式。</i>           比如 <pre> <span class="pln">div</span> <span class="com">#page&gt;div.logo+ul#navigation&gt;li*5&gt;a</span> </pre> 能被扩展成： <pre> <span class="tag">&lt;div</span> <span class="pln"> </span> <span class="atn">id</span> <span class="pun">=</span> <span class="atv">"page"</span> <span class="tag">&gt;</span> <span class="pln"> <br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span> <span class="tag">&lt;div</span> <span class="pln"> </span> <span class="atn">class</span> <span class="pun">=</span> <span class="atv">"logo"</span> <span class="tag">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span> <span class="pln"> <br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span> <span class="tag">&lt;ul</span> <span class="pln"> </span> <span class="atn">id</span> <span class="pun">=</span> <span class="atv">"navigation"</span> <span class="tag">&gt;</span> <span class="pln"> <br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span> <span class="tag">&lt;li&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="pln"> </span> <span class="atn">href</span> <span class="pun">=</span> <span class="atv">""</span> <span class="tag">&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span> <span class="pln"> <br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span> <span class="tag">&lt;li&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="pln"> </span> <span class="atn">href</span> <span class="pun">=</span> <span class="atv">""</span> <span class="tag">&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span> <span class="pln"> <br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span> <span class="tag">&lt;li&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="pln"> </span> <span class="atn">href</span> <span class="pun">=</span> <span class="atv">""</span> <span class="tag">&gt;&lt